name: Sheikh Inu
description: $SHINU It's a meme-utility token which aims to spread crypto culture in Arab region and the world. Marhaba traveller! Welcome to Baba Sheikh’s oasis. A heavenly refueling place for every adventurer seeking treasure. Our aim is unearthing ancient treasures buried in the desert to share evenly with ourcompatriots. Purely meme token driven by our oriental dream to become a group of Sheikh’s we focus on our community to thicken all of our sacks together. Enjoy the elegant breeze of the oasis, feel the odor of the dastarkhan being prepared for you, smoke hookah and feel the sweetness of the exotic fruits served to you. The best is yet to come!
